reviewtext: I apparently already had one and purchased another a few days ago.  Although the box states 12 Mbps on the front, on the back of the package it lists that it has been tested with high speed devices.  Also, on Belkin's website, it also states the cable is 2.0  A quick call to Belkin confirmed that it is 2.0 compatible.
summary: Great deal AND guaranteed at 2.0 by Belkin
